    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>\n                  SARS-CoV-2 transmission occurs via airborne droplets and surface contamination. We show tiles coated with TiO\n                  <jats:sub>2</jats:sub>\n                  120 days previously can inactivate SARS-CoV-2 under ambient indoor lighting with 87% reduction in titres at 1h and complete loss by 5h exposure. TiO\n                  <jats:sub>2</jats:sub>\n                  coatings could be an important tool in containing SARS-CoV-2.\n                </jats:p>",
